name: Moskoni Genesis NFT
description: This is my first work in Tezos.  My name is Moskoni and I live in Madrid.  I am a DJ / Singer & producer.  You can listen to my songs at www.moskoni.com.  I do urban music and I have always liked graffiti and fashion.  Now I'm going to start uploading my works here.  They are graffiti that I do inspired by when I was doing graffiti in my adolescence.  I thank you very much for your support.  This community is great!  I leave my other collections here.  www.candydevilnft.com www.pubksfloyd.org
